                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 812.00/13836.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Belt</persName> to the <gloss
                            type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Mexico City</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1914-11-19">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 19, 1914</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Obregón issued formal declaration of war against Villa tonight. Document given to
                    press tonight late. Obregón expects to leave November 21 for Salina Cruz.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">J. W. Belt</hi>
                    </signed>.</closer>
            </div>
        </body>
